complaint.

39:48.253 --> 39:50.188 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
This is too risky of a thing for
me to do.

39:50.221 --> 39:57.662 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Noreen Farrell,
